1. Casimir 标度预测：
$$
P_C = \frac{C_2(A_2)}{C_2(f)}
= \frac{\frac{k(N-k)(N+1)}{2N}}{\frac{N^2-1}{2N}}
= \frac{k(N-k)(N+1)}{N^2-1}.
$$
对于 $N=4$, $k=2$：
$$
P_C = \frac{2\,(4-2)\,(4+1)}{4^2-1}
= \frac{2\cdot2\cdot5}{15}
= \frac{20}{15}
= \frac{4}{3}.
$$

2. 正弦公式预测：
$$
P_S = \frac{\sin\!\bigl(k\pi/N\bigr)}{\sin\!\bigl(\pi/N\bigr)}
= \frac{\sin(2\pi/4)}{\sin(\pi/4)}
= \frac{\sin(\pi/2)}{\sin(\pi/4)}
= \frac{1}{\tfrac{\sqrt2}{2}}
= \sqrt2.
$$

3. 比率 $Q = P_C/P_S$：
$$
Q = \frac{\tfrac{4}{3}}{\sqrt2}
= \frac{4}{3\sqrt2}
= \frac{2\sqrt2}{3}.
$$
